### CD

- other location -> ubuntu -> var -> www -> html 
- sudo mkdir new
- sudo chown -R jenkins:jenkins /var/www/html/new/

- congigure jenkins job
- add build step -> select "Execute shell"
- cp -r * /var/www/html/new/

- build now

- go to http://0.0.0.0/new/index.html to see the changes


